### B6. Features — Phase 1 (Static MVP)

- Responsive, mobile-first design (320px to 2560px).
- Astro JS static generation with zero layout shift.
- SEO: meta tags, OG tags, JSON-LD schema on all pages.
- Admission enquiry form with email/WhatsApp delivery.
- WhatsApp floating CTA button.
- Google Maps embed on Contact page.
- Gallery with category filter (CSS/JS island).
- Animated hero section (subtle, CSS-only or minimal JS).
- Testimonial carousel.
- Event listing from JSON data file.
- FAQ accordion.
- Google Analytics 4 + Microsoft Clarity.
- Sitemap.xml and robots.txt auto-generated.
- Image optimisation via Astro's built-in Image component.
- Dark-mode ready (optional, Phase 1.5).
- 404 error page, branded.
- Netlify/Vercel deployment with CI/CD from GitHub.

### B7. Features — Phase 2 (Admin Panel)

- Headless CMS (Directus, Sanity, or Strapi) connected via REST/GraphQL API.
- Astro switches from SSG to SSR or ISR (Incremental Static Regeneration).
- Admin can add/edit: events, gallery, blog posts, testimonials, FAQ, staff.
- Enquiry leads dashboard — view, filter, export CSV.
- Online admission form with payment gateway (Razorpay/PayU).
- Parent login portal for fee receipts, circulars, school calendar.
- Push notification for events via WhatsApp Business API.
- Multi-branch support (if school expands).
- Performance analytics dashboard for school management.

### B8. Performance Goals

| Metric | Target |
|---|---|
| Google PageSpeed (Mobile) | >= 90 |
| Google PageSpeed (Desktop) | >= 95 |
| First Contentful Paint | < 1.5s |
| Largest Contentful Paint | < 2.5s |
| Cumulative Layout Shift | < 0.1 |
| Total Blocking Time | < 200ms |
| Bundle Size (JS) | < 50KB gzipped |
| Image Format | WebP with fallback |
| CDN | Netlify Edge / Vercel CDN |
| Lighthouse Accessibility | >= 95 |

### B9. Accessibility Goals

- WCAG 2.1 Level AA compliance.
- All images have descriptive alt text.
- Color contrast ratio >= 4.5:1 for normal text.
- Keyboard navigable — focus states visible.
- ARIA labels on all interactive components.
- Form fields have associated labels and error messages.
- Skip-to-content link on every page.
- Font size minimum 16px body, 14px smallest label.
- Tab order is logical and follows visual hierarchy.

### B10. Risks & Assumptions

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|---|---|---|
| Slow image uploads from school | High | Provide image spec sheet; optimise in CI pipeline |
| Content not ready at launch | Medium | Use placeholder content with clear flagging |
| Admin wants instant CMS in Phase 1 | Medium | Educate on Phase 2 roadmap; offer Netlify CMS as interim |
| Google ranking not quick enough | Medium | Pair with Google Business Profile setup and backlinks |
| Form spam submissions | Low | Honeypot + Netlify spam filtering |
| WhatsApp link format incorrect | Low | Test on Android/iOS before launch |
| School branding assets not available | Medium | Create placeholder brand kit as part of Phase 1 |

