### I2. Metadata Structure

Every page has unique: `<title>`, `<meta name="description">`, canonical URL, Open Graph tags, Twitter Card tags.

**Title Format:**
- Home: "Kiddies Academy | Best Nursery & Primary School in [City]"
- Interior: "[Page Name] | Kiddies Academy [City]"
- Max 60 characters.

**Description Format:**
- Unique per page, 140–160 characters.
- Include primary keyword, CTA snippet, location.
- Example (Admissions): "Admissions open for 2025–26 at Kiddies Academy [City]. CBSE-affiliated. Apply for Playgroup to Grade V. Enquire today."

### I3. Open Graph Tags

| Tag | Value |
|---|---|
| `og:title` | Same as page `<title>` |
| `og:description` | Same as meta description |
| `og:image` | Page-specific 1200×630px image from `/images/og/` |
| `og:url` | Full canonical URL |
| `og:type` | "website" for all pages; "article" for blog posts |
| `og:locale` | `en_IN` |
| `og:site_name` | Kiddies Academy |

### I4. JSON-LD Schema Markup

| Schema | Applied On |
|---|---|
| `EducationalOrganization` | All pages via BaseLayout. Includes name, address, phone, URL, logo. |
| `LocalBusiness` | Home and Contact pages. Includes geo coordinates, opening hours, price range. |
| `FAQPage` | /faq and inline FAQ sections on Admissions. |
| `Event` | Individual event pages (/events/[slug]). |
| `BreadcrumbList` | All interior pages. |
| `Course` | Individual programme pages (/programs/[slug]). |
| `Review / AggregateRating` | /testimonials page. |

### I5. Image Alt Text Strategy

- Every `<img>` has a descriptive, keyword-rich `alt` attribute.
- Formula: `[Action/Subject] + [Context] + [School Name] + [City]`
- Example: "Children playing during Annual Day 2024 at Kiddies Academy, [City]"
- Gallery alt text comes from `gallery.json` "alt" field.
- Team photos: "Teacher [Name], [Role] at Kiddies Academy"
- Facility photos: "[Facility Name] at Kiddies Academy [City]"

### I6. Internal Linking Strategy

- Home links to: all primary pages, top 3 programmes, gallery, testimonials, contact.
- About links to: team, programmes, facilities, admissions.
- Every programme page links to: Admissions, Related activities, Facilities, FAQs.
- Admissions links to: individual programme pages, FAQ, Contact.
- Footer includes links to all main pages on every page.

### I7. Local SEO Strategy (India-Specific)

- **Google Business Profile:** Set up and fully populate with school photos, hours, services.
- **NAP consistency:** Name, Address, Phone identical across website, GBP, Justdial, Sulekha, UrbanPro.
- **Local keywords:** Include city name, area name, pincode in meta descriptions and body copy.
- **Reviews:** Encourage parents to leave Google reviews. Embed Google rating widget on site.
- **Local backlinks:** Get listed on city parenting forums, school directories, JustDial, IndiaStudyChannel.
- **Hindi micro-copy:** Use warmth phrases in Hindi in subheadings or captions for relatability.
- **WhatsApp integration:** Indians trust WhatsApp — feature it prominently.

### I8. Sitemap & Robots

- `sitemap.xml`: Auto-generated by `@astrojs/sitemap`. Includes all pages with priority and changefreq.
- **Priority:** Home = 1.0 | Core pages = 0.8 | Programme pages = 0.9 | Gallery, Events = 0.7 | Blog = 0.6
- `robots.txt`: Allow all crawlers. Disallow `/thank-you`, `/404`, `/api/*`.
- Submit sitemap to Google Search Console and Bing Webmaster Tools on launch day.

